The book is 'Father Nash: Guest Lecture on Prevailing Intercession: How Birthing Revival and Prayer Changes Nations One City at a Time,' and it's by Dr.

00:19:43.435 --> 00:19:44.531
Vince Rizio.

00:19:44.531 --> 00:19:49.205
