00:49:14.891 --> 00:49:15.989
I wept.

00:49:15.989 --> 00:49:17.680
I heaved.

00:49:17.680 --> 00:49:19.262
I cried out.

00:49:28.400 --> 00:49:28.578
The Spirit would come upon me so strongly that words would fail, and all that remained was deep, soundless agony.

00:49:28.578 --> 00:49:33.710
