00:49:47.590 --> 00:49:47.885
You want revival?

00:49:47.885 --> 00:49:51.097
Then pray until heaven groans with you.

00:49:51.097 --> 00:49:53.650
Don't get up until something breaks.

00:49:53.650 --> 00:50:01.975
Most people pray until they get tired, but prevailing intercessors pray until something breaks.

00:50:05.462 --> 00:50:05.711
You stay in that posture.

00:50:05.711 --> 00:50:08.000
You lay on that floor.

00:50:08.000 --> 00:50:12.182
You pour out your guts.

00:50:12.182 --> 00:50:21.980
You wrestle and cry and fast and groan until the heavens crack and the resistance bows.

00:50:24.347 --> 00:50:27.698
The early rain doesn't fall for casual askers; it falls for violent birthers.

00:50:27.698 --> 00:50:31.030
You don't stand up until hell backs down.

00:50:31.030 --> 00:50:33.000
' Did you get that?

