I broke in prayer before the meetings ever began.

00:52:14.800 --> 00:52:19.240
My heart shattered over sin.

00:52:19.240 --> 00:52:21.040
My tears soaked the carpets.

00:52:21.040 --> 00:52:23.840
My strength gave out.

00:52:26.017 --> 00:52:26.326
