00:52:26.634 --> 00:52:28.610
That was where the real battle was won.

00:52:28.760 --> 00:52:35.017
The enemy doesn't tremble at polished sermons; he trembles at broken intercessors.

00:52:35.017 --> 00:52:44.920
I never waited for the warfare to show up; I went ahead and engaged it in prayer before the battle began.

00:52:59.400 --> 00:52:59.640
I would go into towns days early and begin confronting principalities in the spirit.

00:53:09.007 --> 00:53:09.333
The ground would shake in the invisible realm long before the tent ever filled.

00:53:09.333 --> 00:53:12.187
That's why revival fell so hard.

00:53:13.285 --> 00:53:13.610
It was pre-broken.

00:53:19.893 --> 00:53:20.164
The enemy had already been defeated in the unseen realm.

00:53:22.806 --> 00:53:23.234
You want revival to hit like lightning?

00:53:23.234 --> 00:53:26.989
Then strike the ground with prayer before the crowds ever gather.

00:53:26.989 --> 00:53:32.680
Every time I broke in prayer, someone else walked in freedom.

00:53:32.680 --> 00:53:39.248
That's the mystery of intercession.

00:53:39.248 --> 00:53:41.555
Your crushing becomes their freedom.

00:53:41.555 --> 00:53:44.411
When you bleed, others are born.

00:53:44.411 --> 00:53:48.000
When you fall, others rise.

00:53:48.000 --> 00:53:52.140
When you break, revival flows.

00:53:52.140 --> 00:53:54.480
If you're waiting for a stage, you're missing it.

00:53:54.480 --> 00:53:55.800
Find your floor.

00:53:55.800 --> 00:53:58.230
That's where the deliverance begins.

00:53:58.230 --> 00:54:02.480
' And then there are prayers after every chapter.

00:54:02.480 --> 00:54:05.240
It says, 'Father, break me before the breakthrough.

00:54:05.240 --> 00:54:08.769
Let me never run from the pressure that produces your glory.

00:54:08.769 --> 00:54:14.503
I choose to be crushed under the weight of your presence so others can rise in victory.

00:54:14.503 --> 00:54:21.996
Make me a warrior who fights in the spirit before the war is visible.

00:54:21.996 --> 00:54:25.829
Anoint me with preemptive power.

00:54:25.829 --> 00:54:30.050
Let my life be a seed of deliverance.

00:54:30.050 --> 00:54:35.600
Teach me to break in prayer until the heavens open and hell loses its grip.

00:54:35.600 --> 00:54:36.968
' It's beautiful.

00:54:39.333 --> 00:54:39.507
I think that's good tonight.

00:54:39.507 --> 00:54:41.280
Okay, we can read more tomorrow.

00:54:41.280 --> 00:54:47.200
Yeah, there was that one thing you wanted me to read.

00:54:47.200 --> 00:54:48.260
Okay, read it.

00:54:48.260 --> 00:54:56.135
It says, 'Intercession begins when you stop praying about people and start weeping with the heart of God for them.

00:54:56.135 --> 00:54:58.377
' Read it one more time.

00:54:58.377 --> 00:55:04.320
'Intercession begins when you stop praying about people and start weeping with the heart of God for them.

00:55:04.320 --> 00:55:05.160
' Yep.

00:55:11.600 --> 00:55:11.875
And I want to make this clear.

00:55:23.100 --> 00:55:23.330
I do not believe that God put autism on Megan.

00:55:28.804 --> 00:55:29.093
I do not believe that at all.

00:55:29.093 --> 00:55:30.800
It was my ignorance.

00:55:30.800 --> 00:55:42.565
When he said to me, 'Don't get that flu shot,' and I did it anyway, that's when everything went to crap...

00:55:49.751 --> 00:55:49.969
to hell...

00:55:49.969 --> 00:55:53.537
whatever you want to say, it fell apart.

00:55:53.537 --> 00:55:58.760
I'm going to tell you this: It was my ignorance.

00:55:58.760 --> 00:56:01.480
God tried to warn me.

00:56:03.074 --> 00:56:05.611
I knew the day when I walked in there, 'Don't do this.

00:56:05.611 --> 00:56:06.465
' I knew it.

00:56:20.240 --> 00:56:20.531
But I disobeyed because I had fear of the flu virus.

00:56:20.531 --> 00:56:28.147
Because we had friends telling us, 'Your baby could be hospitalized if you don't get this.

00:56:28.147 --> 00:56:34.940
' You listen to the fear, and fear tolerated is faith contaminated.

00:56:36.356 --> 00:56:36.587
It was my fault.

00:56:45.480 --> 00:56:45.760
So, it's not God's fault.

00:56:45.760 --> 00:57:00.360
But what the devil meant for bad, God will turn around for the glory, ladies and gentlemen, if you just lean into him.

00:57:10.560 --> 00:57:11.360
And yes, this has been refining for both of us, but it was by our own ignorance that did this.

00:57:11.360 --> 00:57:12.899
It never was the Lord.

00:57:12.899 --> 00:57:20.005
People go, 'Do you think God caused your daughter to have autism?

00:57:20.005 --> 00:57:20.890
' No.

00:57:23.560 --> 00:57:27.200
The devil and God do not work together.

00:57:27.200 --> 00:57:37.044
And you need to know that they're not up there buddying up together, saying, 'You know what?

00:57:37.044 --> 00:57:39.230
I'll just allow that to happen.

00:57:39.230 --> 00:57:42.480
' No, he specifically said, 'Do not get that.

00:57:42.480 --> 00:57:46.893
Don't put that in her.

00:57:46.893 --> 00:57:50.990
' And I said, 'Diana, I feel a real burden.

00:57:55.940 --> 00:57:56.275
I feel bothered.

00:57:56.275 --> 00:57:57.772
I'll never forget it.

00:58:11.503 --> 00:58:11.817
It was on the way.

00:58:11.817 --> 00:58:14.776
' I said, 'I feel real bothered by this.

00:58:24.220 --> 00:58:26.893
I don't know why, but I just feel this is a huge mistake, but I will do it just in case because of what we've been told.

00:58:26.893 --> 00:58:33.533
' Stupid on our part for ignoring what the Lord told us.

00:58:37.660 --> 00:58:37.830
You know what?

00:58:37.830 --> 00:58:43.010
It was a life lesson, and we learned it.

00:58:43.010 --> 00:58:45.280
But I'm going to tell you, I'll never...

00:58:45.280 --> 00:58:47.560
I'm so thankful for her life.

00:58:47.560 --> 00:58:55.153
I'm so thankful for what I have learned and how it has cultivated both of us to become even better people.

00:59:11.720 --> 00:59:12.040
And we look at people with special needs with more compassion than what we ever could have.

00:59:12.040 --> 00:59:13.920
It cost us something.

00:59:13.920 --> 00:59:15.040
Oh, it did.

00:59:16.640 --> 00:59:23.295
And when we see children with special needs, when we see autistic children, we weep with those families.

00:59:26.253 --> 00:59:26.507
And it is not faked.

00:59:26.507 --> 00:59:36.987
It is a travail, because I know what it's like to be there at that level and see where God has brought us.

00:59:37.533 --> 00:59:44.907
We have seen Megan be potty trained, and we're seeing her come out of where she has been.

00:59:55.013 --> 00:59:55.507
The doctors are even going, "Wow, she's come a long way.

00:59:55.507 --> 00:59:58.320
She's eating good.

00:59:58.320 --> 01:00:05.808
Wow, this is amazing to watch her progress.

01:00:07.232 --> 01:00:11.760
" You know, we give all the glory to Jesus.

01:00:11.760 --> 01:00:19.227
But I always want to tell you, it was never God that did this.

01:00:19.227 --> 01:00:23.940
Always stay on God's side whenever you don't understand what you're going through.

01:00:23.940 --> 01:00:28.260
A lot of times, it's just we're not listening enough.

01:00:28.260 --> 01:00:30.340
We're not yielding enough.

01:00:30.710 --> 01:00:35.010
I just blame myself and I say, "Lord, forgive me.

01:00:35.010 --> 01:00:40.480
But I thank you, Lord, that you're going to turn this into something.

01:00:41.200 --> 01:00:52.286
And it's going to be a testimony to the nations about the goodness of God, that what the devil meant for bad, you're going to turn it around for good.

01:00:52.286 --> 01:01:02.069
And yes, I'm going through this, but God, you will get the glory out of this when it's all said and done.

01:01:16.333 --> 01:01:17.187
" And so, regardless if you blame yourself for maybe a tragic car accident or a very serious thing that your child has gone through, you've got to forgive yourself, for one.

01:01:30.036 --> 01:01:30.387
And it took us a long time to forgive.

01:01:30.387 --> 01:01:43.667
As I was sitting there looking at her even tonight, I looked at her and I said, "Oh, wow," because she had a rough day today.

01:01:43.667 --> 01:01:50.309
And I sat there and I went, "Well, count it all joy.

01:01:50.309 --> 01:01:51.873
Count it all joy.

01:01:51.873 --> 01:01:54.640
I'm not moved by what I see.

01:01:54.640 --> 01:01:56.760
I'm not moved by what I feel.

01:01:56.760 --> 01:02:00.853
I'm moved by what the word of God says.

01:02:06.411 --> 01:02:06.646
" And he said, "By his stripes, we are healed.

01:02:06.646 --> 01:02:11.520
" I am fully persuaded that what God has promised, he's able also to perform it.

01:02:14.783 --> 01:02:16.520
You say, "Well, when is the full manifestation?

01:02:16.520 --> 01:02:17.800
" That's not mine.

01:02:17.800 --> 01:02:20.160
I've released that to him.

01:02:20.160 --> 01:02:27.098
I trust confidently in the finished work of Jesus Christ, and that guarantees me victory.

01:02:27.098 --> 01:02:30.343
We keep going to Billy Burke meetings.

01:02:45.457 --> 01:02:45.760
We go and we get a little piece of the pie every single time.

01:02:52.290 --> 01:02:52.540
We go and we get a little bit more, a little bit more.

01:02:57.840 --> 01:02:58.086
And it's been gradual, but a miracle is a miracle.

01:02:58.086 --> 01:03:00.760
Even if it's gradual, it's progressive.

01:03:00.760 --> 01:03:03.569
Never take baby steps for granted.

01:03:03.569 --> 01:03:14.750
Give God glory in every step you take because it was his grace that gave you the ability to take those steps.

01:03:14.750 --> 01:03:18.200
So, we're going to go to pray now.

01:03:18.200 --> 01:03:32.515
But I just wanted to encourage you all today and just kind of apologize that I missed it a little bit on how I taught that.

01:03:33.065 --> 01:03:36.720
You know, I should have studied a little bit more.

01:03:54.200 --> 01:03:54.420
It was immaturity on my part.

01:04:24.400 --> 01:04:24.703
And so, we brought the scriptures today and we brought the book the lady brought us.

01:04:26.217 --> 01:04:27.549
And so, I hope it blessed you.

01:05:35.720 --> 01:05:36.074
I really do.

01:05:36.074 --> 01:06:06.475
This book will change your life.

01:06:06.475 --> 01:07:08.690
We're going to read it probably every month now.

01:07:08.690 --> 01:07:27.703
I told her, I said, "Well, we just found our next best book.

01:07:27.703 --> 01:07:31.250
We'll read that book because of where we're called.

01:07:31.250 --> 01:07:33.731
We'll read that every single month.

01:07:33.731 --> 01:07:35.240
" I'm not kidding.

01:07:35.240 --> 01:07:37.640
She'll read it to me in the car.

01:07:37.640 --> 01:07:39.949
You've got to keep your fan flamed.

01:07:39.949 --> 01:07:41.206
Fan your flame.

01:07:55.940 --> 01:07:56.200
Don't let it get stagnant.

01:07:58.858 --> 01:07:59.089
You don't want to leak out.

01:08:48.086 --> 01:08:48.349
And you've got to keep full and let your full fight for you.

01:08:48.349 --> 01:08:51.120
And you've got to keep that fan flamed.

01:08:51.120 --> 01:09:18.703
So I want you to really take this to heart.

01:09:18.703 --> 01:09:19.828
All right.

01:09:19.828 --> 01:09:23.125
Well, I feel like that was good.

01:11:06.680 --> 01:11:06.982
We went right on with that one.

01:11:06.982 --> 01:11:07.889
All right.

01:11:07.889 --> 01:11:44.520
Well, you know, yesterday when we prayed, we saw the glory in Cuba, and we saw that dragon over North Korea, and we saw where we're at in time.

01:11:44.520 --> 01:11:46.046
Honey, 50:50?

01:11:46.046 --> 01:11:48.949
Ah, too long talking.

01:11:48.949 --> 01:12:43.907
We saw the dragon over North Korea.

01:12:43.907 --> 01:12:44.849
We saw Michael.

01:12:56.491 --> 01:12:57.006
The Lord showed me Michael with the opal-looking breastplate on.

01:12:57.006 --> 01:13:02.773
And I'm telling you, Michael is massive.

01:13:21.260 --> 01:13:21.590
The Lord said, "That's Michael.

01:13:21.590 --> 01:13:33.624
" He lassoed that dragon that had its wings over North Korea, and he started pulling that dragon by the neck.

01:13:33.624 --> 01:13:58.773
And like, you know how you'd see a cattle wrestler, they rope those steers by the horns and they pull that thing down.

01:13:58.773 --> 01:14:06.578
I saw Michael lasso that principality over North Korea.

01:14:06.578 --> 01:14:16.680
It was a massive red dragon with huge wings, and it was hovering over it like, "This is mine.

01:14:16.680 --> 01:14:27.415
" And Michael grabbed hold and pulled that dragon off by the neck and ripped him straight off that land.

01:14:27.415 --> 01:15:37.298
And I'm telling you, freedom and liberty are coming to the people of North Korea.

01:15:37.298 --> 01:15:47.431
Jesus is going to have a major revival there.

01:16:43.891 --> 01:16:44.280
And we're going to see the greatest outpouring over that nation in the name of Jesus, and we will continue to intercede until Kim Jong-un is dealt with.

01:18:07.725 --> 01:18:08.000
The Lord said, "Do not let this up.

01:18:09.857 --> 01:19:11.106
You keep at it until this is a greasy spot.

01:19:11.106 --> 01:19:25.933
I'm believing Kim Jong-un is going to be removed, and his sister.

01:19:25.933 --> 01:19:36.308
" And the Lord said, "It will not be by military force.

01:19:36.308 --> 01:19:47.720
It will be by my hand.

01:19:47.720 --> 01:19:56.175
Just like I dealt with Pharaoh, I will deal with this man.

01:19:56.175 --> 01:20:06.893
" And he said, "I have not forgotten the people of North Korea, the people of Asia.

01:20:06.893 --> 01:20:12.347
Their cries cry out before me.

01:20:12.347 --> 01:20:17.480
" And if you remember, I saw the prayers.

01:20:17.480 --> 01:20:36.824
They came before him as tears, and they were all before his throne, and he gathered them up before him, and he brought them to his chest.

01:20:37.272 --> 01:20:40.496
Do you remember that?

01:20:49.360 --> 01:20:49.800
And I'm telling you, I feel major breakthrough is coming for North Korea.

01:21:05.840 --> 01:21:06.080
I believe it.

01:21:11.546 --> 01:21:12.728
It's time.

01:21:13.920 --> 01:21:19.571
And as we saw Cuba last night, there were three major wells.

01:21:19.571 --> 01:21:22.171
Three major wells of revival.

01:21:36.290 --> 01:21:40.782
And those wells were one in each part: one in the far west, one in the middle, and one toward the east.

01:21:42.120 --> 01:21:56.974
And each one of them was a springing well that was bringing forth water.

01:21:56.974 --> 01:22:23.801
And it looked like a geyser.

01:22:23.801 --> 01:22:50.230
It was a gusher of water.

01:22:50.240 --> 01:24:03.230
And the Lord said, "This is a fountain that will never run dry.

01:25:16.480 --> 01:25:16.724
" And I saw churches that were being birthed around this well.

01:25:21.920 --> 01:25:22.205
And I saw a woman that had leathered skin.

01:25:27.040 --> 01:25:29.871
And she had a cloak, like a prayer shawl over her head that looked Jewish.

01:25:29.871 --> 01:25:31.780
She was travailing and interceding.

01:25:31.780 --> 01:25:36.360
And as the revival started to break forth in Cuba, she was weeping before the Lord.

01:25:38.893 --> 01:25:41.690
I bet this lady was probably—in the vision, she was probably 90 years old.

01:25:41.690 --> 01:25:47.600
But she was travailing for the country to have a major revival in Cuba.

01:25:47.600 --> 01:25:55.147
As I saw this, I saw a witchcraft spirit that was thick over the nation.

01:26:11.800 --> 01:26:12.130
And the Lord said, "I'm breaking the back of the witchcraft upon Cuba.

01:26:13.780 --> 01:26:19.709
" And as I saw the witchcraft departing, it looked like a parting of a storm.

01:26:19.709 --> 01:26:24.200
I saw the glory of the Lord come upon the land of Cuba.

01:26:29.707 --> 01:26:29.902
And I saw Maldonado.

01:26:29.902 --> 01:26:31.620
Sorry, I'm not good with names, Maldonado.

01:26:31.620 --> 01:26:34.068
He is a pastor of the Miami church.

01:26:34.068 --> 01:26:43.330
He's invited me to a lot of these places to go with him and minister.

01:26:47.116 --> 01:26:47.684
And he is the one that's over at the White House.

01:26:47.684 --> 01:26:51.000
He said, "Brandon, I already have the largest church in Cuba.

01:26:53.130 --> 01:27:00.629
" Because I contacted him after the prayer and I said, "This is what the Lord showed me about your ministry.

01:27:00.629 --> 01:27:03.793
You're going to have missionary teams go there.

01:27:04.027 --> 01:27:08.720
" And he said to me, "I already have the largest church in Cuba.

01:27:11.409 --> 01:27:15.651
" And I said, "Well, you'll have two more, and that'll be these other two wells.

01:27:24.800 --> 01:27:25.480
" I believe that's what I was seeing in the spirit.

01:27:30.440 --> 01:27:32.818
I saw creative miracles of arms growing out, eyes coming back, dead being raised.

01:27:36.080 --> 01:27:42.120
And the Lord said the greatest harvest of souls that Cuba has ever known is about to spring forth.

01:27:42.120 --> 01:27:44.560
He said, "Be ready, pastors.

01:27:50.773 --> 01:27:51.076
Be ready, those that speak Spanish, for when the door opens, he wants you to flood the land.

01:27:55.860 --> 01:27:56.055
You're going to flood this land.

01:28:06.520 --> 01:28:06.971
" And I saw a major move of people flooding over into Cuba.

01:28:06.971 --> 01:28:14.580
And it wasn't just about spiritual blessing; it was about financial.

01:28:14.580 --> 01:28:20.280
The Lord said he was restoring the fountains of wealth.

01:28:20.280 --> 01:28:25.240
It was like a third-world country that was no more.

01:28:25.240 --> 01:28:27.336
It was like America.

01:28:35.742 --> 01:28:35.905
The blessing was on the land of Cuba.

01:28:37.424 --> 01:28:40.320
I saw hotels, I've told you, the car industry—all these major things were coming.

01:28:40.980 --> 01:28:44.278
And the Lord said, "I'm liberating the people of Cuba.

01:28:51.771 --> 01:28:51.989
" And I saw who was leading the charge; it was Secretary of State Rubio.

01:29:25.278 --> 01:29:25.877
The Lord said, "Pray for Rubio.

01:29:25.877 --> 01:29:32.335
Marco Rubio.

01:29:32.335 --> 01:29:40.335
Pray for him.

01:29:40.335 --> 01:29:47.815
Pray for him.

01:29:47.815 --> 01:30:01.275
" And I saw revival coming to Mexico.

01:30:01.275 --> 01:30:17.590
And so, Maldonado—I'm sorry, Guillermo.

01:30:17.600 --> 01:30:26.428
I'll just say Guillermo.

01:30:26.428 --> 01:30:39.715
It's easier to say.

01:30:39.715 --> 01:31:11.860
I always try to call him by his last name, Guillermo.

01:31:11.860 --> 01:31:22.160
He said, "I'm on my way to Argentina.

01:31:22.160 --> 01:31:27.310
Please pray for me.

01:31:27.320 --> 01:31:54.093
" He said we're going to have a major revival, and I'm believing it because he's there right now.

01:31:54.093 --> 01:32:13.973
He texted me when he landed, and he said, "I'm here.

01:32:13.973 --> 01:32:20.540
We're starting our meetings.

01:32:47.560 --> 01:32:47.800
" And he said they're believing for healings and demonstrations.

01:32:47.800 --> 01:34:06.560
So we are going to pray for Guillermo tonight for this revival that he is going to hold all week long in Argentina, for a major outpouring over South America, for this to be the beginning of the transfer.

01:34:06.560 --> 01:34:59.000
Because the Lord told me through this, he said, "You will see this begin in the month of April.

01:34:59.000 --> 01:35:56.190
" You're going to start to see it, and I gave him this privately, and I told him months ago.

01:37:32.960 --> 01:37:45.550
And I'm telling you, as he's there right now in Argentina, he said, "I have 23 nations that I'm going to this year before the doors start to close and the things happen before the end of the end.

01:37:45.550 --> 01:38:46.480
" I'm telling you, folks, we are on the verge of the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen before.

01:38:46.480 --> 01:39:00.185
But it's going to take people like you and me praying for people like him right now in Argentina, believing for a major harvest.

01:39:00.185 --> 01:39:10.137
So let's lift him up before the Lord, and we will pray for this harvest, that they'll have signs and wonders.

01:39:10.137 --> 01:39:13.966
They're going to see creative miracles, dead raised.

01:39:13.966 --> 01:39:15.700
He is a fire-breathing preacher.

01:39:15.700 --> 01:39:20.338
And so I'm telling you, I believe that God is going to use this man, and the Lord told me he was.

01:39:20.338 --> 01:39:27.486
And so I believe we're going to see great signs for them this week in Argentina.

01:39:27.486 --> 01:39:30.520
Another part is praying for Mike Lindell.

01:39:38.880 --> 01:39:39.016
The Lord lifted up Mike Lindell to me, and he said to pray for his health specifically, concerning his body.

01:39:39.424 --> 01:39:43.980
The enemy would try to take him out with health complications so that he couldn't be the governor of Minnesota.

01:39:44.744 --> 01:39:47.293
And the Lord said, "Intercede for him against attacks on his health.

01:39:48.851 --> 01:39:49.343
" You understand?

01:39:49.343 --> 01:39:53.720
So, we're going to lift him up again.

01:40:02.000 --> 01:40:12.238
I don't feel complete release from that, so we're going to pray for that.

01:40:26.707 --> 01:40:28.173
And we're going to pray for the storms.

01:40:40.212 --> 01:40:49.156
I saw a major tornado coming up.

01:41:35.686 --> 01:41:37.012
We are under tornado warnings and watches right now here in Oklahoma.

01:41:37.012 --> 01:41:49.413
What I saw is actually happening.

01:41:49.413 --> 01:42:20.000
And we're believing for five inches of rain, but not destructive hail and wind and things like that.

01:42:20.000 --> 01:43:02.670
And so, praying over Israel, praying over the straits, praying over the protection of our troops on the ground.

